Sample_growth_protocol_ch1: We grew melanoma cell lines (WM989 and WM983B) from the lab of Meenhard Herlyn in Tu2% media containing 78% MCDB, 20% Leibovitz’s L-15 media, 2% FBS, and 1.68mM CaCl2.
Sample_extract_protocol_ch1: We performed ATAC sequencing on WM989-A6 melanoma cells according to Buenrostro et al. Briefly, we lysed the cells and set up the transposition reaction with the Tn5 Transposes (Illumina Catalog #FC121-1030) at 37℃ for 30 minutes. We cleaned the reaction with a Qiagen MinElute Kit and then amplified the libraries using custom Nextera PCR primers.
Sample_data_processing: We aligned our reads to hg19 with bowtie2, HOMER package for peak calling, differential peak calling, motif analysis, and gene ontology analysis
